md:
giải nghĩa từ "deliver" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

** Deliver **

* Verb: giao, chuyển, đưa, giao hàng, chuyển giao
* Example: "The company will deliver the goods to your doorstep."
* Related words: delivery, deliverable, delivered

** Deliver ** ( Verb )

* Giao: "The post office will deliver the package to your address."
* Chuyển: "The company will deliver the goods to the warehouse."
* Đưa: "The teacher will deliver the lesson to the students."
* Giao hàng: "The online store will deliver the products to your home."
* Chuyển giao: "The company will deliver the project to the new team."

** Delivery ** ( Noun )

* Giao hàng: "The delivery of the package was delayed."
* Chuyển giao: "The delivery of the project was successful."

** Deliverable ** ( Noun )

* Sản phẩm giao: "The deliverable of the project is a working software."
* Kết quả giao: "The deliverable of the meeting is a report."

** Delivered ** ( Verb )

* Đã giao: "The package has been delivered to your doorstep."
* Đã chuyển: "The goods have been delivered to the warehouse."
* Đã đưa: "The lesson has been delivered to the students."
* Đã giao hàng: "The products have been delivered to your home."
* Đã chuyển giao: "The project has been delivered to the new team."
